#: ../../source/advanced/specification.rst:40
msgid "Perisomatic Modelとは"
msgstr "What is the Perisomatic Model?"

#: ../../source/advanced/specification.rst:42
msgid ""
"Perisomatic modelは、`Allen Cell Types Database <https://celltypes.brain-"
"map.org/>`_ で採用されている生物物理学的ニューロンモデルの一種です。このモデルには以下の特徴があります："
msgstr ""
"Perisomatic model is a type of biophysical neuron model used in `Allen Cell Types Database <https://celltypes.brain-"
"map.org/>`_. This model has the following characteristics:"

#: ../../source/advanced/specification.rst:44
msgid "**定義と構造:**"
msgstr "**Definition and Structure:**"

#: ../../source/advanced/specification.rst:46
msgid "**イオン伝導度の配置**: 主要なイオンチャネルは細胞体（soma）周辺に配置されます"
msgstr "**Ion conductance placement**: Major ion channels are placed around the cell body (soma)"

#: ../../source/advanced/specification.rst:47
msgid "**詳細な形態**: 実際のニューロンから再構築された形態データを使用"
msgstr "**Detailed morphology**: Uses morphological data reconstructed from actual neurons"

#: ../../source/advanced/specification.rst:48
msgid "**簡略化された軸索**: 実際の軸索形態の代わりに、人工的な簡易軸索が付与されます"
msgstr "**Simplified axon**: An artificial simplified axon is given instead of the actual axon morphology"

#: ../../source/advanced/specification.rst:50
msgid "**モデルの目的:**"
msgstr "**Model Purpose:**"

#: ../../source/advanced/specification.rst:52
msgid "**発火特性の再現**: マウス視覚野や人間の皮質における異なる細胞タイプの発火特性を正確に再現"
msgstr "**Reproduction of firing properties**: Accurately reproduce the firing properties of different cell types in mouse visual cortex and human cortex"

#: ../../source/advanced/specification.rst:53
msgid "**多様性の理解**: ニューロンの多様性を計算モデルで表現し、理解を深める"
msgstr "**Understanding diversity**: Express and deepen understanding of neuronal diversity through computational models"

#: ../../source/advanced/specification.rst:54
msgid "**汎化性能**: 抽象的なモデルよりも、異なるタイプの入力に対してより自然に汎化できる"
msgstr "**Generalization performance**: Generalizes more naturally to different types of inputs than abstract models"

#: ../../source/advanced/specification.rst:56
msgid "**技術的詳細:**"
msgstr "**Technical Details:**"

#: ../../source/advanced/specification.rst:58
msgid "**最適化手法**: 遺伝的アルゴリズムを用いてパラメータを最適化"
msgstr "**Optimization method**: Parameters are optimized using genetic algorithms"

#: ../../source/advanced/specification.rst:59
msgid "**訓練データ**: 段階電流刺激（step current injection）への応答に基づいて訓練"
msgstr "**Training data**: Trained based on response to step current injection"

#: ../../source/advanced/specification.rst:60
msgid "**実装**: `NEURON <https://www.neuron.yale.edu/>`_ 環境で実装され、Allen SDKを通じて利用可能"
msgstr "**Implementation**: Implemented in `NEURON <https://www.neuron.yale.edu/>`_ environment and available through Allen SDK"

#: ../../source/advanced/specification.rst:63
msgid ""
"このモデルはBMTKでの定義同様に、**人工的な簡易軸索が付与される** "
"ことに注意してください。これは計算効率とモデルの安定性を保つための設計上の選択です。"
msgstr ""
"Please note that **an artificial simplified axon is provided** as in BMTK definitions. "
"This is a design choice to maintain computational efficiency and model stability."

#: ../../source/advanced/specification.rst:66
msgid ""
"Allen Instituteの公式ドキュメント: `Perisomatic Single Neurons <https://brain-"
"map.org/our-research/computational-modeling/perisomatic-biophysical-"
"single-neuron-models>`_"
msgstr ""
"Allen Institute official documentation: `Perisomatic Single Neurons <https://brain-"
"map.org/our-research/computational-modeling/perisomatic-biophysical-"
"single-neuron-models>`_"

